SABRE Fighter Plane Simulator
Windows NT/95 Version 0.2.3 Patch

This is a patch to update your SABRE Fighter Plane
installation to Version 0.2.3. If you have not
previously downloaded SABRE, this patch will not
work!

The full distribution of SABRE Fighter
Plane Simulator is available at:
http://sabre.cobite.com

